      Whether it's with friends, family, or a clubhouse packed with Deaf patrons, this app takes care of everything for you.
      </p>
      <header class="text-center py-8">
        <h1 class="font-bold text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-6xl">
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-fuchsia-500 to-purple-700 text-transparent bg-clip-text">No subscriptions.</span> <br>
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-violet-600 text-transparent bg-clip-text">No fees.</span> <br>
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-fuchsia-500 to-purple-700 text-transparent bg-clip-text">No contracts.</span> <br>
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-violet-600 text-transparent bg-clip-text">No licensing.</span>
        </h1>
      </header>



    <p class="text-4xl">
      <strong>Free forever.</strong>
    </p>
    <br /><br/>
      
