    <br /><br />
      The purpose of this app is to modernize the classic DINGO game and make it as popular as ever, through accessible and convenient means.
    <br /><br />
      You had to find a club hosting a DINGO game to play...<br /><strong>now you can play with friends anywhere!</strong>
    </p>
    </Fragment>
  </Hero>
  
